    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_FB782E60-2222-0135-7343-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If your Canvas admin has enabled self enrollment for your institution, you can enable self enrollment in your course. Self-enrollment allows a student to sign up for a course using a secret URL or code. Self-enrollment can be enabled for a course whether or not the course is publicly visible. </p>
<p><strong>Notes</strong>: </p>
<ul>
<li>If you cannot view the options for self enrollment, your admin has disabled this setting for your institution.</li>
<li>Instructors are not notified when a student self-enrolls.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_settings" data-step-uuid="0F1B0C2D-ECAA-44CA-9797-8FC07D358691">
