  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FB78F2F0-2222-0135-7345-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_course_details" data-step-uuid="a503aae0-8977-4dc3-8f99-ea70b1cc1ffb">
