    <p>Click the <strong>Course Details </strong>tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="enable_self_enrollment" data-step-uuid="69EADEEE-1F24-4B71-8B3F-F47F105BB1BC">
    <h2 id="enable_self_enrollment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Enable Self-Enrollment</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/361/216/original/96e57c5a-149d-4717-8a15-3572600ef0db.png" srcset="" alt="Enable Self-Enrollment" height="169" width="486">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FB7A4060-2222-0135-734B-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Let students self-enroll by sharing with them a secret URL or code</strong> checkbox.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="add_join_the_course_link" data-step-uuid="11194bb4-b730-44e1-9d39-21d14ed12ccd">
    <h3 id="add_join_the_course_link" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Join the Course Link</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/361/218/original/a06ef2ad-f2a6-4cef-bb55-a152a28a2471.png" srcset="" alt="Add Join the Course Link" height="166" width="483">
